{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require broadcasters to have BSL interpretation for all news broadcasts",
        "additional_details": "The Government should make signing compulsory for all news channels. This should help deaf people access the news and feel less isolated.",
        "background": "Not all deaf people can read subtitles or lip read, and therefore can be excluded by broadcasts that do not include British Sign Language (BSL). This is a particular issue during the pandemic since we are all under lockdown and are particularly reliant on broadcast news.",
